
Technical Specification Document (TSD)

Regression Automation Framework using AWX / Ansible Tower

Version: 1.0

Status: Draft

Owner: Automation Platform Team

---

1. Purpose

This document defines the technical architecture, framework design, execution model, reporting model, and operational behavior of the Regression Automation Framework implemented using AWX (Ansible Tower) and Ansible.

The framework provides a reusable platform for deployment, execution, validation, reporting, and recovery of regression testing activities across multiple applications and artifacts.

